casebody.data:
Benjamin Lee HUBBARD, Appellant,
v.
Tiffany Yvonne HUBBARD, Respondent. WD 80728 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. Filed: July 24, 2018 Rebecca J. Martin, Kansas City for appellant. Gail Berkowitz-Gifford; Preston A. Drobeck, Kansas City for respondent. Before Division Two: Mark D. Pfeiffer, Presiding Judge, Lisa White Hardwick and Edward R. Ardini, Jr., Judges

ORDER

Per Curiam Benjamin Hubbard appeals from the judgment dissolving his marriage to Tiffany Hubbard. Upon review of the briefs and the record, we find no error and affirm the judgment. We have provided the parties with a Memorandum explaining the reasons for our decision, because a published opinion would have no precedential value.

AFFIRMED. Rule 84.16(b).
